title: 'For Rs 160/- the Vega branded scissors are fine
rating: and just about manage to do the required ...'
column5: For Rs 160/- the Vega branded scissors are fine, and just about manage to do the required job. They are however not a top quality item. The front 1 inch of the scissor does not cut as either the blades are dull or misaligned. The blades are also ''loose'' and they had to be tightened up by the provided screw that holds them together.
